  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two hands! Lots of fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two Hands Egg is just a normal egg...except for the fact that it has two hands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also turn into an egg and run, jump, and swim!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/0c2175c916a2497c72fb87efd5db05ef.poster.avif?t=1754582231\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/0c2175c916a2497c72fb87efd5db05ef.webm?t=1754582231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/0c2175c916a2497c72fb87efd5db05ef.mp4?t=1754582231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All you need to do is use the two sticks on the controller.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you tilt the stick, the hand moves in conjunction with the stick.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you hit the ground with your hand, you will jump.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can do various movements such as walking by rotating your hand like a tire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Stage mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 stages each in 4 worlds (grass, ice, water, volcano)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/cd691801d99c7dd88fb2c06887f81c62.poster.avif?t=1754582231\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/cd691801d99c7dd88fb2c06887f81c62.webm?t=1754582231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/cd691801d99c7dd88fb2c06887f81c62.mp4?t=1754582231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Party mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-4 player mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are two types at the start of early access.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sumo</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mode where you defeat your opponent!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The last egg remaining is the winner! !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Volleyball</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Volleyball using an egg-shaped ball!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many types of balls and courts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rubber Band Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/69b280c1ab46d772377e4b13ffd66354.poster.avif?t=1754582231\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/69b280c1ab46d772377e4b13ffd66354.webm?t=1754582231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/69b280c1ab46d772377e4b13ffd66354.mp4?t=1754582231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obsessed with rubber bands</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We help each other, but sometimes we get in each other's way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About Live Streaming</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please feel free to use the site for commercial or non-commercial purposes.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two hands! Lots of fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two Hands Egg is just a normal egg...except for the fact that it has two hands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also turn into an egg and run, jump, and swim!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/0c2175c916a2497c72fb87efd5db05ef.poster.avif?t=1754582231\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/0c2175c916a2497c72fb87efd5db05ef.webm?t=1754582231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/0c2175c916a2497c72fb87efd5db05ef.mp4?t=1754582231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All you need to do is use the two sticks on the controller.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you tilt the stick, the hand moves in conjunction with the stick.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you hit the ground with your hand, you will jump.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can do various movements such as walking by rotating your hand like a tire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Stage mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 stages each in 4 worlds (grass, ice, water, volcano)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/cd691801d99c7dd88fb2c06887f81c62.poster.avif?t=1754582231\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378490/extras/cd691801d99c7dd88fb2c06887f81c62.webm?t=1754582231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\">